title: Hour 2 - Jimmy G. Trending
itunes:title: Hour 2 - Jimmy G. Trending
description:
Covino & Rich are filling in for Dan Patrick and look at the Baker news from the Browns perspective. Is Brissett the answer while Watson serves a suspension? Could Jimmy G. be a band-aid? The show also talks Russell Wilson/Ciara, Broncos, AFC and NFC West and Aaron Rodgers gets ink!
